Class PathPrimitiveList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.contentmine.graphics.svg.path.PathPrimitiveList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<SVGPathPrimitive>

    public class PathPrimitiveList
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<SVGPathPrimitive>
    Container and manager for primitives from an SVGPath. being developed to manage compression for dense paths (NYI) For some reason I cannot understand a normal ArrayList has appalling performance

    pm286
